{
  "id": "RAW_419940a2",
  "title": "我们给你做了一个「有洞」的充电宝，想让你的充电体验有点「不一样」",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzU4Mjg3MDAyMQ==&mid=2247601659&idx=1&sn=b9a5f5bf53d18f9480f8c47e3dca8a64",
  "date": "2025-12-17 04:22:00",
  "author": "少数派",
  "siteName": "少数派",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p><img src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=78be297f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRhkiaEfBIS8zEnTVicOaAzz2iaGC0KwxFv4IMskB6FaDkwTwwT8JiarFuzlicPVromfLcVl7zhIrs4hpmw%2F0%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">在工业设计这个行当里，设计师通常不仅不喜欢洞，甚至讨厌洞。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">理由很简单：一个孔，意味着灰尘会进去，水会进去，内部杂乱的电路板会露出来。所以，大多数电子产品一直致力于追求——「密封」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">但如果你回头看过去六十年的产品历史，你会发现「孔」并没有消失。相反，它从一个不得已而为之的功能缺陷，逐渐演变为标准接口，最后甚至成为装饰符号。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">要理解为什么现在的手机壳和充电宝上会有洞，我们需要把时间轴推回到 1950 年代。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">第一阶段：不得不打的孔</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">代表人物：迪特·拉姆斯（Dieter Rams）关键词：秩序、散热、不可触碰</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">上世纪五六十年代，德国博朗（Braun）的设计师迪特·拉姆斯面临一个很实际的物理问题：电器要工作，就会发热；收音机要出声，扬声器就不能被完全挡住。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">而那时候没有液冷散热，也没有现在的导音技术。外壳开孔是必然选择。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">拉姆斯的做法非常「德国」。既然必须开孔，那就让它极致规整。以经典的 T3 袖珍收音机为例，正面的扬声器区域布满了121个微小的圆孔。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100118001\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"873\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f8ad683b&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRhkiaEfBIS8zEnTVicOaAzz2iarEgqa1KATc419brgnOooTE5X1D4Whw29ib8LlKkmibpFYYLG5CJCiatdw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">T3 袖珍收音机</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这些孔有两个特点：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">极度规律</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">：它们排列成严格的几何方阵，孔距分毫不差。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">拒绝交互</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">：这些孔纯粹是为了机器的运作。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这种设计传递出精密、冷静的工业美学，直到今天，MacBook 键盘两侧的扬声器开孔仍延续这种思路——只为功能，不容误差。</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">第二阶段：把墙面变成网格</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">代表物品：洞洞板 关键词：标准、收纳、通用性</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">到了二战后的美国，另一种「孔」在车库和五金店里流行起来：在硬质纤维板上按 1 英寸间距打孔，它就变成了一套通用收纳系统。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">洞洞板的出现成为工业设计史上一个重要的转折：标准化接口的诞生。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">只要孔距是标准的，你就可以去商店买任何品牌的挂钩、置物篮、甚至弹力绳。你不需要为了挂一把新锤子而在墙上钻个新孔。从此，这类设计从车库走向全球家居，成为收纳的核心逻辑。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100118005\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dbdf554d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRhkiaEfBIS8zEnTVicOaAzz2iabLVebiaYMiamsZMPwFiaicITbFibX5quUKgwxpDcAQlicb5fz9RszmE26Qfg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">宜家 SKÅDIS 系列产品</span></span></p>\n  <h2 style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;h3&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;ss-hIdChildren-1&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;line-height: 1.75em; margin-bottom: 24px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;s1&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;color: rgb(255, 76, 65);\">▍</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;\">第三阶段：意外的装饰品</span></span></h2>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">代表品牌：Crocs（卡骆驰）关键词：插件、个性、反叛</span></span></strong></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">2005 年，孔的设计逻辑发生了第三次变化。这次变化源于一次「意外」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">因为这双鞋原本是为划船设计的，所以 Crocs 刚推出时，鞋面上的那几个大洞纯粹是为了排水和透气。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">直到一位名叫 Sheri Schmelzer 的家庭主妇将自制饰件塞进孔中，将功能性「孔洞」转变为「个性化表达接口」——Jibbitz（智必星）由此诞生。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100118004\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.84375\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=e98e2f56&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRhkiaEfBIS8zEnTVicOaAzz2iaQZcO0YLFU1sU9w41asrKhcSUzzMQHGGl8WLToiaUtBvLvYhbGafJicMw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 12px;color: rgb(84, 84, 84);\">Crocs（卡骆驰）产品装饰效果</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这件事彻底改变了厂商的思路。孔的意义从此改变：它成为展示个性的插槽。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这是一种权力的反转。在第一阶段，设计师说了算；在第二阶段，为了实用妥协；到了第三阶段，用户拥有了最终解释权。我想插卡通公仔，还是插字母标语，完全看我今天的心情。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">少数派「扭扭宝」：电子产品的开放式设计</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">梳理完这三个阶段，我们再来看少数派新推出的「扭扭宝」，就能明白它的设计逻辑是从哪来的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">现在的充电宝，绝大多数设计还停留在追求“严丝合缝”第一阶段。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">扭扭宝反其道而行之。它采用了类似 Crocs 的“第三阶段”设计思路——开放接口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">这款产品刚刚通过了新国标 3C 安全认证，它在设计上有三个很明显的特征：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">物理留白</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">： 机身采用了非对称设计。电芯和电路板集中在顶部的圆柱体内（厚度 27.4mm），而下半部分是一块极薄的金属板，厚度只有 4.5mm。 设计师在这块金属板上，直接预留了</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">6 个标准的圆形孔位。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100118003\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.55625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2f363cff&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRhkiaEfBIS8zEnTVicOaAzz2iaro2nXbfM2PJG0uVCdsLLy16Ba6XhazLfBU3c9eQXuTtxFYdvEau9aw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">把「定义权」交给用户</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">： 这 6 个孔没有电气功能，不散热也不导电。它们就是为了让你“扭”东西的。 你可以像玩洞洞鞋一样，把配套的装饰扣扭进去；也可以自己用 3D 打印机做一个支架；甚至可以挂上一串钥匙。它把冷冰冰的数码配件，变成了一个可以 DIY 的 EDC（日常携带）装备。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">扭扭宝的 6 个孔洞，每个的直径在 9mm，深度 4mm，可以支持任何通过螺丝拧紧的配件。此次我们精选了来自「奇妙洞物」的八款正版迪士尼配件作为赠品。让你在上手充电宝的时刻就能很好的装饰它。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100118000\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.58125\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=4aad7fa2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRhkiaEfBIS8zEnTVicOaAzz2ia7o0kuG0pNib2RM7vmTWYxLib5ia3T4SGI6wfFTV7BNMRic6dDPzavKy53A%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">同时我们还附赠了一张少数派 logo 贴纸，让你可以自由搭配你的风格。以下是来自深圳后海汇少数派线下店搭配好的实拍图：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100118006\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=45b58e79&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRhkiaEfBIS8zEnTVicOaAzz2ia4yicsugRqwLjExPEHdQaYEWhDb07fpKqNWbbiaERo3zaPibaSBrfDm1KQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;font-weight: bold;\">基础素质的保留</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">： 在好玩之外，它依然是一个合格的充电工具。5000mAh 的容量，支持 20W 有线快充和 15W 无线磁吸。146g 的重量，吸在 iPhone 背面时，因为底部很薄，握持起来不会觉得手里多了一大块异物。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100118002\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6741071428571429\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"webp\" data-w=\"1120\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d944f510&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fsz_mmbiz_jpg%2Foylw20gGnRhkiaEfBIS8zEnTVicOaAzz2iaiaOnqraOnswbavmECZicN6LaWRAUiaGsc3JWY0m0Guv5ibyd4OQYYODBEg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dwebp%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">现在这款充电宝已正式发售，欢迎点击下方链接选购：</span></span></p>\n  <p class=\"mp_common_product_iframe_wrp\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><mp-common-product data-windowproduct=\"v1=HGrHmuNDP65nxJEJOln7x12A0xQATGa54TMMT6NeDSYbuYBBcQFAajD5_EkV73ItKhPt1Q\" data-cardtype=\"0\" data-title=\"少数派 扭扭宝 磁吸洞洞充电宝个性化定制自由搭配\" data-type=\"0\"></mp-common-product></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">从博朗的精密网格，到扭扭宝的装饰孔位，工业设计并没有变得越来越复杂，反而变得越来越「松弛」。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"line-height: 1.75em;margin-bottom: 24px;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;letter-spacing:0.034em;font-size:17px;font-family:mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-style:normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;\">扭扭宝就是这种松弛感的产物。它不强迫你接受某种高深的美学，它只是留了几个孔，问你：「你想在这里放点什么？」</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">原文链接：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://sspai.com/post/104627?utm_source=wechat&amp;utm_medium=social\" target=\"_blank\">https://sspai.com/post/104627?utm_source=wechat&amp;utm_medium=social</a></span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 5px;margin-left: 8px;font-family: mp-quote, -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;caret-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);text-size-adjust: auto;line-height: normal;\"><span style=\"caret-color: rgb(84, 84, 84);color: rgb(84, 84, 84);font-size: 12px;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者：什么陈</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-right: 8px;margin-left: 8px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;text-wrap: wrap;text-align: center;margin-bottom: 16px;\">\n   <br>\n  </p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章以工业设计中“孔”的演变为线索，深入剖析少数派“扭扭宝”充电宝通过开放式设计赋予用户个性化定制权利的创新理念。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章以工业设计中“孔”的演变为线索，深入剖析少数派“扭扭宝”充电宝通过开放式设计赋予用户个性化定制权利的创新理念。",
  "summary": "文章通过回顾工业设计史上“孔”的三阶段演变，从迪特·拉姆斯为功能而设的规整散热孔，到洞洞板作为标准化收纳接口的通用孔，再到 Crocs 鞋面孔洞演变为个性化装饰插槽。在此基础上，引出少数派新推出的“扭扭宝”充电宝，阐述其如何借鉴 Crocs 的设计理念，通过预留物理孔位，将电子产品从封闭式设计转变为开放式、可定制化产品，赋予用户 DIY 的权力，从而改变用户与产品的互动关系，让数码配件更具个性与趣味。同时，文章也强调了“扭扭宝”在创新设计的同时，仍保留了充电宝的基础实用功能。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "工业设计中“孔”的演变体现了设计理念从功能驱动到用户驱动的转变。",
      "explanation": "从迪特·拉姆斯的功能性规整孔，到洞洞板的标准化接口，再到 Crocs 鞋面孔洞的个性化表达，这一历程展现了设计思维如何从满足基础需求转向赋能用户创造。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“扭扭宝”充电宝借鉴开放式设计理念，将电子产品变为用户可 DIY 的个性化载体。",
      "explanation": "通过在产品上预留无功能的标准孔位，允许用户自由搭配装饰件或定制配件，突破了传统电子产品的封闭性，增加了产品的趣味性和用户参与感。"
    },
    {
      "point": "个性化与实用性兼顾是创新消费电子产品的关键。",
      "explanation": "“扭扭宝”在提供独特个性化体验的同时，仍确保了充电宝作为核心功能的稳定性和便利性（如快充、无线充电、轻薄设计），提升了产品的综合吸引力。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "如果你回头看过去六十年的产品历史，你会发现「孔」并没有消失。相反，它从一个不得已而为之的功能缺陷，逐渐演变为标准接口，最后甚至成为装饰符号。",
    "孔的意义从此改变：它成为展示个性的插槽。这是一种权力的反转。在第一阶段，设计师说了算；在第二阶段，为了实用妥协；到了第三阶段，用户拥有了最终解释权。",
    "扭扭宝就是这种松弛感的产物。它不强迫你接受某种高深的美学，它只是留了几个孔，问你：「你想在这里放点什么？」"
  ],
